title: [SOLVED] 820-2936-B PM_SLP_S4_L problem
message:
Hello Everybody

I m working on liquid damaged 820-2936-B SMC area around, cleaned by ultrasonic now fan spin and turn off loop.

Stable voltages :
PPBUS_G3H 12.5V 
PP3V3_S5 3.3V
PPVRTC_G3H 3.3V

But PM_SLP_S4_L up 3v and down 0

Already replaced SMC and looked bad parts nothing changed, any idea for next step?

Thanks.

title: [SOLVED] 820-2936-B PM_SLP_S4_L problem
message: PM_SLP_S4_L is created by the PCH not the SMC. what does U1800 look like?

title: [SOLVED] 820-2936-B PM_SLP_S4_L problem
message:
U1800 will look like a PCH.

U2800 will be the first suspect here, replace.
